Package: nseval
Type: Package
Title: The Missing API For Non-Standard Evaluation in R
Version: 0.4
Date: 2018-04-07
Author: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Description: A clean API for metaprogramming in R. Facilities to
             capture, create, and manipulate calls, lazy arguments
             (promises), and `...` lists.
